palestine_surveys.messages:
We‚Äôll ask 3 quick questions first üí¨
This helps us share tips that are right for families like yours üíîüïäÔ∏è
Thank you so much for participating in these tips! You are so brave and such an amazing caregiver.
Today you will receive your final tips. First, we have 3 questions to ask about how you and your children are doing. ‚ù§Ô∏è
Over the last week, how often have you been bothered by feeling down, depressed, or hopeless?
Over the last week, how often have you been bothered by little interest or pleasure in doing things?
How many days in the past week did you play with your children or help them learn something new?

Before we continue, would you like to answer 5 quick questions? üìù

Your answers will help us make these tips better for parents and children finding strength and hope during war, displacement, and other tough times üíîüå±
palestine_surveys.stop.conditions.1.message: That's ok, you will get more tips tomorrow.

palestine_surveys.messages: How many days in the past week did you do something to keep your child(ren) safe, such as make sure they don't spend time alone with unknown adults/children or walk home alone outside after dark?
How many days in the past week did you shout, yell, or scream at your child(ren)?
How many days in the past week did you discipline your child(ren) physically, such as hitting them with your hand or another object?
How many days in the past week did you try to speak calmly with your child when you were upset with them?
How many days in the past week did you have a meaningful conversation with your child(ren) about how they‚Äôre doing amidst the current war, displacement, and other tough times?

Just 2 more quick questions üí¨
This helps us give tips that truly help parents like you.
What is your home nationality?
How long have you been displaced from your home?
Thank you for answering ‚ô•Ô∏è  We‚Äôll see you back for the next tip soon üëè
Lastly, today we want to ask 2 questions to make these tips better for others üéâ
Did these parenting tips help you and your family during war, displacement or other tough times?
palestine_surveys.choices.1.text: Yes, ALL of the tips helped
palestine_surveys.choices.2.text: Yes, MANY of the tips helped
palestine_surveys.choices.3.text: Yes, a FEW of the tips helped
